00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.500
<c.dialog>"Tokubechu, Shite"</c>

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:15.500
<c.dialog>"Tokubechu, Shite", released last year, has surpassed
2.1 billion cumulative views on TikTok.</c>

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:23.000
<c.dialog>The brand-new show that will uncover the uniqueness
and true nature of each member starts tonight!</c>

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.500
<c.dialog>=LOVE KO KO KO!!</c>

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:47.500
<c.dialog>This show will bring out the maximum potential</c>

00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:51.500
<c.dialog>and uniqueness of each member.</c>

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:54.000
<c.dialog>We are Aiseki Start, your MCs. Nice to meet you!</c>

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.500
<c.dialog>Nice to meet you!</c>

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.500
<c.dialog>Kei-san, this is your first time meeting them, right?</c>

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:02.000
<c.dialog>- Yes, this is our first time meeting.
- Nice to meet you.</c>

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:05.000
<c.dialog>I hope we can get closer from now on,</c>

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:08.000
<c.dialog>and be able to call each other by nicknames.</c>

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.500
<c.dialog>In this premiere episode, the member whose
uniqueness we will uncover is...</c>

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:13.500
<c.dialog>Our group's leader, Yamamoto Anna!</c>

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.500
<c.dialog>Please take care of me!</c>

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.500 position:80% line:20%
<c.editor-yellow>【Uniqueness】
Knows the most about the members</c>

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:22.000
<c.dialog>=LOVE's leader, Yamamoto Anna,
will give a presentation about the members!</c>

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
<c.dialog>Moreover...</c>

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:27.500
<c.dialog>- Are these videos really from your phone?
- Yes, they are.</c>

00:01:27.500 --> 00:01:34.000
<c.dialog>We will show treasure-like photos and videos
of the members saved on Yamamoto's phone!</c>

00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:37.000
<c.dialog>These have never been published before.</c>

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:42.000
<c.dialog>Don't miss these rare moments shown
for the first time in this 30-minute episode!</c>

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:48.000
<c.dialog>Could you tell us
what kind of person Leader Yamamoto is?</c>

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.000
<c.dialog>Her nickname is "Ankoro Mochiko"!</c>

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.500
<c.dialog>I have about 10 nicknames.</c>

00:01:52.500 --> 00:01:55.000
<c.dialog>I also brought a drawing of my face...</c>

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.500
<c.dialog>Wow, amazing!</c>

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:00.500
<c.dialog>It looks just like you.</c>

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:02.500
<c.dialog>Did you draw it yourself?</c>

00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:04.500
<c.dialog>Yes. It's a self-portrait.</c>

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:09.000
<c.dialog>"Anya" at the very top is
my official nickname,</c>

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:13.000
<c.dialog>and from there, each member
calls me by different names.</c>

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:16.000
<c.dialog>I have the most nicknames in this group.</c>

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:19.000
<c.dialog>So your leader status is just in name,
and you're actually underestimated quite a bit?</c>

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:23.000
<c.dialog>- I get teased a lot...
- A loveable leader!</c>

00:02:23.500 --> 00:02:26.500
<c.dialog>Since I also don't know much about you guys yet,</c>

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:29.000
<c.dialog>I'd like the leader to introduce the other members.</c>

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:31.000
<c.dialog>Leave it to me!</c>

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:35.000
<c.dialog>Alright, let's start with Sasaki Maika.</c>

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.000
<c.dialog>Here is Sasaki Maika! Ta-da!</c>

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:42.500
<c.dialog>First, she is like a miraculous being
created by God.</c>

00:02:42.500 --> 00:02:48.500
<c.dialog>Her visual is everyone's dream,
and her voice is very stable when singing.</c>

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:52.500
<c.dialog>She is also thoughtful and
cares a lot about others.</c>

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:57.000
<c.dialog>But, as the leader,
I won't just praise her!</c>

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:01.000
<c.dialog>- There's a warning sign!
- That part can be peeled off!</c>

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:05.000
<c.dialog>I'll reveal it. Ta-da!</c>

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:11.500
<c.dialog>"She hates calling to make food reservations,
so please order for her."</c>

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:16.500
<c.dialog>"The person attending the outdoor rehearsal
might not be the real Maika."</c>

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:18.500
<c.dialog>She doesn't participate in the rehearsal?</c>

00:03:18.500 --> 00:03:20.500
<c.dialog>I have a photo...</c>

00:03:20.500 --> 00:03:23.000
<c.dialog>- This has been published before, right?
- Never!</c>

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:27.000
<c.dialog>- Oh!
- From the leader's personal collection!</c>

00:03:27.500 --> 00:03:31.000
<c.dialog>We are showing this for the first time!</c>

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:36.000
<c.dialog>A photo of Sasaki's outdoor concert rehearsal
taken by Yamamoto herself!</c>

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:39.000
<c.dialog>Huh? What's with that?</c>

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:44.000
<c.dialog>This was during the outdoor concert rehearsal,
"probably" the real Sasaki Maika.</c>

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:46.500
<c.dialog>We can't see her face at all.</c>

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:49.000
<c.dialog>You can verify it's me from my nail art.</c>

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:57.000
<c.dialog>Last year, my outfit was much darker.
The mouth area was also black.</c>

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.500
<c.dialog>But because it was too scary,
I used white this year.</c>

00:04:00.500 --> 00:04:03.000
<c.dialog>How is this any better than last year!</c>

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.500
<c.dialog>Such a rare photo.</c>

00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:08.000
<c.dialog>Everyone better be prepared!
Brace yourselves.</c>

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.500
<c.dialog>Let's move on.</c>

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:13.500
<c.dialog>Next is Noguchi Iori!</c>

00:04:13.500 --> 00:04:19.500
<c.dialog>She has a loud voice, and her way of speaking...
let's just say it's not very polite.</c>

00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:23.000
<c.dialog>However, she is the most serious
and a perfectionist.</c>

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:27.500
<c.dialog>It seems like you have no flaws,
do you have any bad sides?</c>

00:04:27.500 --> 00:04:29.000
<c.dialog>Yes, there is.</c>

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.000
<c.dialog>I'll reveal it. Ta-da!</c>

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:36.500
<c.dialog>Not as "Noguchi Iori", but when she becomes "I-chan"
she turns into a "Bratty Kid".</c>

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:39.500
<c.dialog>- Shut up!
- Oh, that's her bratty behavior.</c>

00:04:39.500 --> 00:04:46.000
<c.dialog>Here is the footage of Noguchi that successfully
proves Yamamoto's "Bratty Kid" nickname!</c>

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.000 position:80%
<c.editor>Not an
Idol's Face</c>

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.000
<c.dialog>What kind of idol face is that?
What's wrong with you?</c>

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
<c.dialog>Is it okay to air this?</c>

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.000
<c.dialog>You look like you're involved in something illegal.</c>

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.000
<c.dialog>Yeah. It's really scary.</c>

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:10.000
<c.dialog>So at that time, I asked her to hold my phone,</c>

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:12.500
<c.dialog>and when she returned it, this video was in my gallery.</c>

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:16.000
<c.dialog>Since she secretly recorded this,
I decided to expose her.</c>

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:19.500
<c.dialog>It really is a video from the leader's phone.</c>

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.500
<c.dialog>Yes, it is.</c>

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:24.000
<c.dialog>Next is Takamatsu Hitomi.</c>

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:30.000
<c.dialog>This rare photo will reveal her other side
that only Yamamoto knows!</c>

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:35.000
<c.dialog>She has a smile as bright as the sun,
and a strong spirit to lead the group.</c>

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:39.000
<c.dialog>Even though she's the third youngest,
she has a mature side like an older sister.</c>

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:44.500
<c.dialog>But... behind that, the real Hitomi is...</c>

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:48.500
<c.dialog>And actually, she is...</c>

00:05:48.500 --> 00:05:51.500
<c.dialog>Please take a look at this photo.</c>

00:05:52.500 --> 00:05:55.000
<c.dialog>Wow, the photo is so aesthetic.</c>

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.500
<c.dialog>- Looking a bit pretentious, right?
- Yeah, acting cool.</c>

00:05:58.500 --> 00:06:05.000
<c.dialog>She even wears sunglasses while strolling around.
Just like a celebrity.</c>

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.500
<c.dialog>Even though she looks very fashionable and elegant...</c>

00:06:07.500 --> 00:06:11.500
<c.dialog>A while ago, when we were staying at a hotel out of town,</c>

00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:17.500
<c.dialog>she sent a message, "Anna, can I come to your room?
Can I use your shower?"</c>

00:06:17.500 --> 00:06:22.000
<c.dialog>That's kinda cute.
But why so suddenly?</c>

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:26.500
<c.dialog>So, she only dares to act cool while the sun is still up.</c>

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:31.500
<c.dialog>But once the sun goes down,
she doesn't even dare to shower alone.</c>

00:06:32.500 --> 00:06:34.500
<c.dialog>Hitomi, why did you go to the leader's room?</c>

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:38.000
<c.dialog>I felt like I could somewhat sense "that thing"...</c>

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.000
<c.dialog>- You have a sixth sense?
- Yes.</c>

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:45.000
<c.dialog>Since I felt the hotel was a bit creepy,
and I couldn't bear to be alone...</c>

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:47.000
<c.dialog>I ran to Anna's room.</c>

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:49.500
<c.dialog>At times like that, the leader is very reliable, huh?</c>

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:51.500
<c.dialog>Right! I'm so happy.</c>

00:06:51.500 --> 00:06:54.000
<c.dialog>You are really relied upon, Yamamoto.</c>

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.500
<c.dialog>Yes, she's a true leader.</c>

00:06:56.500 --> 00:07:00.000
<c.dialog>Next is... Ta-da! Morohashi Sana.</c>

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:03.000
<c.dialog>Hey, who is that!?</c>

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:05.500
<c.dialog>The teeth are huge!</c>

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:09.500
<c.dialog>Sana is known for her toothy smile, right!</c>

00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:13.500
<c.dialog>Her nickname is "Sanatsun".</c>

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:20.500
<c.dialog>During MC breaks at concerts, just her talking
brightens up the mood and makes everyone smile.</c>

00:07:20.500 --> 00:07:23.000
<c.dialog>But this Sana...</c>

00:07:23.500 --> 00:07:30.500
<c.dialog>She does her makeup until the very last minute before a concert,
and always... cuts it super close.</c>

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:39.000
<c.dialog>Here is a video of Sana right before a live performance,
recorded and edited by Yamamoto herself!</c>

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:42.000
<c.dialog>Of course, this is a world premiere!</c>

00:07:42.500 --> 00:07:47.000
<c.dialog>Sana started eating 5 minutes before the concert.</c>

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.500
<c.dialog>This is really bad...</c>

00:07:48.500 --> 00:07:50.000
<c.dialog>Let's go, to the stage.</c>

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.500
<c.dialog>Can I get one more serving?</c>

00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:55.500
<c.dialog>I've worked for 8 years,
and this is the first time someone eats 5 minutes before going on stage.</c>

00:07:55.500 --> 00:07:57.000
<c.dialog>Want some?</c>

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.000
<c.dialog>Hell no!</c>

00:07:59.500 --> 00:08:02.000
<c.dialog>This is an actual video of the incident?</c>

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:05.000
<c.dialog>I happened to record it during the recent tour...</c>

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:08.000
<c.dialog>Even though the time right before a live is crucial...</c>

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:11.000
<c.dialog>Right. Sometimes we are so busy we don't even eat.</c>

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:15.500
<c.dialog>But when I hear the audience's cheers,
my stomach starts growling.</c>

00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:18.500
<c.dialog>I don't understand your thought process.
Hearing cheers makes you...</c>

00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:24.500
<c.dialog>You should shorten your makeup time,
and use the rest to eat... manage your time better.</c>

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:27.500
<c.dialog>I wish I could...</c>

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:30.500
<c.dialog>Let's move on to the next member.</c>

00:08:30.500 --> 00:08:33.000
<c.dialog>Next is, ta-da! Otani Emiri!</c>

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:35.000
<c.dialog>She is every girl's dream.</c>

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:40.000
<c.dialog>If Mirinya says it's cute,
it must be cute! She is very reliable!</c>

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:42.500
<c.dialog>But!</c>

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:47.000
<c.dialog>Ta-da! Sometimes she arrives at the venue
with soaking wet hair.</c>

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.500
<c.dialog>It's true!</c>

00:08:48.500 --> 00:08:50.000
<c.dialog>She's soaking wet today too!</c>

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:54.500
<c.dialog>What do you mean? By the way,
speaking of that famous scary story,</c>

00:08:54.500 --> 00:09:01.000
<c.dialog>about a taxi picking up a female passenger, suddenly she disappears
and the seat is soaking wet. You know that scary story, right?</c>

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:05.500
<c.dialog>Could that woman be you?</c>

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:10.500
<c.dialog>Also, she always goes home empty-handed,
carrying only natto in her pocket.</c>

00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:14.000
<c.dialog>Please take a look at the photo.</c>

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:17.500
<c.dialog>This was right after a concert ended...</c>

00:09:17.500 --> 00:09:21.000
<c.dialog>If it's a 2-day concert schedule,
we can leave our belongings there.</c>

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:25.000
<c.dialog>But while others carry small bags
or paper bags when going home...</c>

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:28.000
<c.dialog>This girl says "Thanks for your hard work"
and goes home looking like this.</c>

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:35.000
<c.dialog>From the photo, she looks like a thug
who would ride shotgun in a recklessly driven car.</c>

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:43.000
<c.dialog>The difference between when she's dolled up cute
and when she's not is huge.</c>

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:46.500
<c.dialog>Yeah, I'm really a sloppy and messy person.</c>

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:50.000
<c.dialog>Next member, Otoshima Risa.</c>

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:54.000
<c.dialog>Yamamoto has something
she really wants to say today...</c>

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:59.000
<c.dialog>When her dance is caught on camera, her wink
successfully steals everyone's heart.</c>

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:04.000
<c.dialog>Her style is amazing, she is a true idol.</c>

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:10.000
<c.dialog>But! It's about time you inherited that title.</c>

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:14.000
<c.dialog>Please look at this photo.</c>

00:10:14.500 --> 00:10:18.500
<c.dialog>It's a very cute photo. Carrying a beautiful bag too.</c>

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:25.500
<c.dialog>In the group, I don't know since when
I started being called "High Brand Woman".</c>

00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:35.000
<c.dialog>But honestly, from the leader's perspective,
the true High Brand Woman is actually Otoshima Risa!</c>

00:10:35.500 --> 00:10:41.000
<c.dialog>So the leader kept this a secret all this time!
She willingly became the sole scapegoat.</c>

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:46.500
<c.dialog>Look at this photo!
It's a cute bag from a famous brand...</c>

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:49.500
<c.dialog>But the price is not cute at all!</c>

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:56.500
<c.dialog>It's very precious to me, because I bought it
exactly on Ichiryumanbaibi (a lucky day) and Taian (the most auspicious day).</c>

00:10:56.500 --> 00:11:01.000
<c.dialog>Such old-fashioned customs
won't justify its exorbitant price!</c>

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:05.000
<c.dialog>Am I really seen as someone who loves branded goods?
My collection isn't even that big...</c>

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:08.500
<c.dialog>The one who buys branded goods the most
is definitely the leader!</c>

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:11.000
<c.dialog>Ah, I can feel the sparks flying!</c>

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:14.000
<c.dialog>Everyone, please close your eyes.</c>

00:11:14.500 --> 00:11:19.000 line:20%
<c.rule>=LOVE's High Brand Queen</c>

00:11:14.500 --> 00:11:19.500
<c.dialog>Let's hold a vote to determine
who the =LOVE High Brand Queen is!</c>

00:11:19.500 --> 00:11:23.000
<c.dialog>Who will be
the true High Brand Queen?</c>

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:29.000
<c.dialog>Those who agree that Yamamoto is the High Brand Queen,
please raise your hand.</c>

00:11:29.500 --> 00:11:34.000
<c.dialog>Yes, yes. You may lower your hands.</c>

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:41.000
<c.dialog>Those who agree that the =LOVE High Brand Queen is
Otoshima, please raise your hand.</c>

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:47.000
<c.dialog>Okay, the decision is unanimous.
Everyone, please open your eyes.</c>

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:51.000
<c.dialog>The High Brand Queen is the leader!</c>

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.500
<c.dialog>What the heck!?</c>

00:11:52.500 --> 00:11:55.000
<c.dialog>You're kidding, right!?</c>

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:58.500
<c.dialog>Absolute majority. It's a huge margin.</c>

00:11:58.500 --> 00:12:00.500
<c.dialog>It's definitely you!</c>

00:12:00.500 --> 00:12:06.500
<c.dialog>Even though I told the manager today,
"Today I'm passing the High Brand Queen title to Risa!"</c>

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:09.500
<c.dialog>Impossible!</c>

00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:15.500
<c.dialog>You really know how to do variety shows!
Your true colors are showing.</c>

00:12:15.500 --> 00:12:18.500
<c.dialog>It seems it's still too early
for Risa to inherit this title.</c>

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:20.500
<c.dialog>Yeah, you just keep that title!</c>

00:12:20.500 --> 00:12:22.500
<c.dialog>I've returned it to you.</c>

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:28.000
<c.dialog>- Shall we continue?
- Yes. Next is Takiwaki Shoko!</c>

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:31.000
<c.dialog>Wow, so cute!</c>

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:36.500
<c.dialog>Lately she's been taking a lot of dance lessons
and has grown tremendously!</c>

00:12:36.500 --> 00:12:40.000
<c.dialog>I'm also the weakest to Shoko's tears...</c>

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:42.000
<c.dialog>Does she cry easily?</c>

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:46.000
<c.dialog>Not really, she's not the type
to cry easily in her daily life.</c>

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:51.500
<c.dialog>That's why when she does cry, it touches my heart
and makes me want to protect her...</c>

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:54.000
<c.dialog>This Shoko turns out to...</c>

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:59.000
<c.dialog>"Messages asking 'What are you doing?' at night
must be replied to immediately."</c>

00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:03.000
<c.dialog>Recently, I kept her company on a call for 4 hours!</c>

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:07.000
<c.dialog>From 12 AM to 4 AM.</c>

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:12.500
<c.dialog>12 AM is usually
bedtime, right?</c>

00:13:12.500 --> 00:13:18.500
<c.dialog>When I look at her schedule for tomorrow,
"Oh, Anna seems to be free."</c>

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:21.000
<c.dialog>Such a hassle!</c>

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:27.000
<c.dialog>Enough already. Are you satisfied now?</c>

00:13:27.500 --> 00:13:35.000
<c.dialog>Yamamoto captured the moment the clingy Takiwaki
was being clingy to another member!</c>

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:42.000
<c.dialog>So clingy, right.
This is when she was acting clingy with Sana.</c>

00:13:42.500 --> 00:13:45.000
<c.dialog>Is this moment very rare? Like hugging...</c>

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:55.000
<c.dialog>Usually I'm not clingy at all.
My clingy side only comes out at night...</c>

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:59.000
<c.dialog>I was also called by her at that time,</c>

00:13:59.000 --> 00:14:04.000
<c.dialog>but when I was about to hang up, she said,
"Please don't hang up! Don't hang up!"</c>

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:08.500
<c.dialog>Because I had to wake up at 5 AM then,</c>

00:14:08.500 --> 00:14:14.000
<c.dialog>I said, "Sorry, but please call Anna instead!"
So I passed the buck to Anna.</c>

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:19.500
<c.dialog>You guys are really close.
Truly proof of your closeness.</c>

00:14:19.500 --> 00:14:23.000
<c.dialog>Next... Ta-da! Oba Hana!</c>

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:29.000
<c.dialog>Her voice, her dance, her way of talking, everything!
She can make everyone smile.</c>

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:34.500
<c.dialog>About Hana... I also have something.
Ta-da!</c>

00:14:34.500 --> 00:14:43.000
<c.dialog>"Because she was too absorbed in giving fanservice to the audience,
she was late returning to the stage, and got scolded by the staff."</c>

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:49.000
<c.dialog>When I arrived on stage,
Sana came up to me angrily.</c>

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:58.500
<c.dialog>While I was dancing happily, Sana said
"You don't realize the time, do you!" like that.</c>

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:10.500
<c.dialog>I was quite down at that time.
Felt really guilty because I couldn't get back...</c>

00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:16.500
<c.dialog>In the end, I performed the rest of the song
full of guilt.</c>

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:19.500
<c.dialog>You must have regretted it a lot.</c>

00:15:19.500 --> 00:15:25.500
<c.dialog>Your story makes us want to watch your concert live.
To see moments like that.</c>

00:15:26.500 --> 00:15:33.500
<c.dialog>Since I've already talked about her flaws,
I want to share a rare video of her sleeping in the dressing room,</c>

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:36.500
<c.dialog>sleeping cutely like a baby.</c>

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:44.000
<c.dialog>Here is Yamamoto's secret recording,
the sleeping face of the always-cheerful Oba is rarely seen!</c>

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:48.000
<c.dialog>A rare video that's only 4 seconds long!</c>

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:54.000
<c.dialog>It's so rare to see Hana sleeping
in the dressing room... So short!</c>

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:57.000
<c.dialog>You intentionally recorded it secretly, right?</c>

00:15:57.000 --> 00:16:01.000
<c.dialog>That day I suddenly felt so sleepy,
so I just fell asleep.</c>

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:05.000
<c.dialog>It means you were exhausted.
That's why you could be recorded secretly like that.</c>

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:11.000
<c.dialog>Since I exposed the story of her getting scolded earlier,
maybe I should neutralize the situation here.</c>

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:12.500
<c.dialog>Next is the last one, right?</c>

00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:16.000
<c.dialog>The last member is Saito Kiara!</c>

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:18.500
<c.dialog>Our youngest member.</c>

00:16:18.500 --> 00:16:23.000
<c.dialog>She used to be like a cute little sister to all of us,
but now she's a strong, reliable idol.</c>

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:25.500
<c.dialog>But!</c>

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:28.500
<c.dialog>She is the center of comedy in this group.</c>

00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:33.000
<c.dialog>We have a large collection of hilarious photos and videos of Kiara.</c>

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:37.000
<c.dialog>99% of them are videos not suitable for public broadcast.</c>

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:44.000
<c.dialog>But... among all of those, there is a hilarious video of her
that's still within acceptable limits to be shown.</c>

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:45.500
<c.dialog>What video?</c>

00:16:45.500 --> 00:16:50.000
<c.dialog>Challenge: "Get up without using your hands!"</c>

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:55.000
<c.dialog>What is this?</c>

00:16:56.500 --> 00:16:58.500
<c.dialog>Ouch!</c>

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:02.500
<c.dialog>Where was that and what were you doing?</c>

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:07.500
<c.dialog>This was during our free time,
there happened to be a bed in the room,</c>

00:17:07.500 --> 00:17:11.000
<c.dialog>so I challenged her,
"Kiara, try getting up without using your hands!"</c>

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:14.500
<c.dialog>And then she innocently kept trying...</c>

00:17:14.500 --> 00:17:21.000
<c.dialog>I felt like I had to succeed, because if I did
the video would be super cool!</c>

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:28.000
<c.dialog>Even though I tried so hard, I still couldn't do it...
You should try it yourself at home.</c>

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:34.000
<c.dialog>I'm not interested. This is the one within "acceptable limits"?
It means you have a lot of unacceptable things going on.</c>

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:36.000
<c.dialog>This is still much better, right?</c>

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:40.000
<c.dialog>If you challenge me like that,
I'd definitely do anything.</c>

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:46.500
<c.dialog>Wow, it's really different when it's the leader...
Amazing, almost all of them are rare videos.</c>

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:50.000
<c.dialog>Even though she only introduced herself
through her nicknames.</c>

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:55.500
<c.dialog>In the end, the High Brand Queen title
flew right back at her like a boomerang.</c>

00:17:55.500 --> 00:18:01.000
<c.dialog>Right! Now my titles are just
nicknames and High Brand Queen!</c>

00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:05.500
<c.dialog>Everyone respects you a lot,
that has been conveyed clearly.</c>

00:18:05.500 --> 00:18:09.500
<c.dialog>And! The =LOVE lineup order
that I created is this!</c>

00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:16.500
<c.dialog>The =LOVE lineup order created by Yamamoto Anna
will be uploaded on our show's social media accounts!</c>

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:31.000
<c.dialog>Up next, a song performance with Yamamoto as the center
that is full of the uniqueness of each =LOVE member!</c>

