<c.dialog>♪ Hugging tight, then becoming cute ♪</c>

00:18:35.293 --> 00:18:36.293
<c.dialog>♪ (Oh yeah!) ♪</c>

00:18:36.293 --> 00:18:38.307
<c.dialog>♪ Gotta be number one ♪</c>

00:18:38.307 --> 00:18:39.089
<c.dialog>♪ (Oh yeah!) ♪</c>

00:18:39.089 --> 00:18:41.001
<c.dialog>♪ An L sign with the right hand, =LOVE ♪</c>

00:18:41.001 --> 00:18:41.584
<c.dialog>♪ (Oh yeah!) ♪</c>

00:18:41.584 --> 00:18:44.209
<c.dialog>♪ Ooh... Yeah! ♪</c>

00:18:44.209 --> 00:18:45.667
<c.dialog>♪ A cute and charming mermaid ♪</c>

00:18:45.667 --> 00:18:47.126
