00:19:29.889 --> 00:19:33.001
<c.dialog>♪ A spoiled gap, an unfair person everyone falls for ♪</c>

00:19:33.001 --> 00:19:38.459
<c.dialog>♪ L-O-V-E, Noguchi Iori ♪</c>

00:19:38.459 --> 00:19:41.126
