00:19:41.126 --> 00:19:43.234
<c.dialog>♪ Taking on any challenge, an active Girl ♪</c>

00:19:43.234 --> 00:19:46.459
<c.dialog>♪ A hardworking figure, BPM up ♪</c>

00:19:46.459 --> 00:19:51.667
<c.dialog>♪ L-O-V-E, Takiwaki Shoko ♪</c>

00:19:51.667 --> 00:19:54.626
<c.dialog>♪ "=LOVE is the best! Let's enjoy it!" ♪</c>

00:19:54.626 --> 00:19:57.417
