00:19:57.417 --> 00:19:59.232
<c.dialog>♪ it's a happy ending ♪</c>

00:19:59.232 --> 00:20:00.540
<c.dialog>♪ You and I! ♪</c>

00:20:00.540 --> 00:20:02.834
<c.dialog>♪ Where is this love heading? ♪</c>

00:20:02.834 --> 00:20:05.354
