00:20:05.354 --> 00:20:10.461
<c.dialog>♪ =LOVE came to see you! (Yeah!) ♪</c>

00:20:10.461 --> 00:20:14.695
<c.dialog>♪ Wave your hands, wave your hands more!! ♪</c>

00:20:14.695 --> 00:20:16.168
