00:20:44.287 --> 00:20:47.224
<c.dialog>♪ Packing love into her candy voice ♪</c>

00:20:47.224 --> 00:20:52.606
<c.dialog>♪ L-O-V-E, Saito Kiara ♪</c>

00:20:52.606 --> 00:20:55.084
<c.dialog>♪ "Dyukushi!" into everyone's hearts ♪</c>

00:20:55.084 --> 00:20:57.375
<c.dialog>♪ Here we are! Our leader ♪</c>

00:20:57.375 --> 00:21:01.003
<c.dialog>♪ Lil lil girl, yet, ill ill dancing ♪</c>

00:21:01.003 --> 00:21:06.023
<c.dialog>♪ L-O-V-E, Yamamoto Anna ♪</c>

00:21:06.023 --> 00:21:08.758
<c.dialog>♪ "A homerun into your heart" ♪</c>

00:21:08.758 --> 00:21:11.177
<c.dialog>♪ Princess, princess, where are you? ♪</c>

00:21:11.177 --> 00:21:13.772
<c.dialog>♪ Captivating everyone with her enchanting voice ♪</c>

00:21:13.772 --> 00:21:17.110
<c.dialog>♪ In charge of green, she will sing for you ♪</c>

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:22.105
