00:21:40.498 --> 00:21:43.450
<c.dialog>♪ Don't be shy ♪</c>

00:21:43.450 --> 00:21:46.060
<c.dialog>♪ I wanted to see you ♪</c>

00:21:46.060 --> 00:21:48.981
<c.dialog>♪ I've been waiting for today all along ♪</c>

00:22:02.709 --> 00:22:06.651
<c.dialog>Everyone in the Arena, how are you doing? (Yeah!)</c>

00:22:07.625 --> 00:22:12.001
<c.dialog>♪ Thank you for dressing up nicely ♪</c>

00:22:12.001 --> 00:22:13.501
<c.dialog>♪ (I just you!) ♪</c>

00:22:13.501 --> 00:22:17.834
<c.dialog>♪ Even from afar, I can feel the love ♪</c>

00:22:17.834 --> 00:22:18.334
<c.dialog>♪ Because... ♪</c>

00:22:18.334 --> 00:22:23.417
<c.dialog>♪ Your one and only heroine is!? ♪</c>

00:22:23.417 --> 00:22:25.375
<c.dialog>♪ [=LOVE] ♪</c>

00:22:25.375 --> 00:22:27.042
<c.dialog>♪ Hugging tight, then becoming cute ♪</c>

00:22:27.042 --> 00:22:28.251
<c.dialog>♪ (Oh yeah!) ♪</c>

